OOC: Unless otherwise stated, my posts will have the G1 Razorclaw .
BIC:
Razorclaw listened to the message that was telling them to head east, but 
his instincts told him to wait for the object that was coming from the west. 
  His sensors indicated that the signature was familiar yet altered.

Divebomb stated, "Galvatron?...can it be?..."

Razoclaw replied, "No...this signature is strange.  Let us wait to see whom 
it belongs to..." With that he transformed into his lion form.

The other predacons followed suit and tranformed into thier beast modes as 
well.  They all took strategic positions and waited...
